divs: sighting detailsi was parked on a street in long island city which is located in queens new york. the street i was parked on at the time is between the mid-town tunnel(which leads into manhattan)and the long island expressway. i adjusted my seat to lean back giving me a clear view of the sky which was overcast at the time. no soon as i looked at the sky a dark\black triangle ufo flew overhead and was out of sight in seconds. i knew right away that it was one of the triangle ufo's that have been reported in the mid-west and western states. it wasn't the large 'mother ship' reported, this was the smaller version. like i mention it was triangle in shape and seemed to glide effortlessly through the air. the had a dull dark\black color to it, hand not lights emitting from it, it seemed to be smooth. it was so low that if it were a conventional plane i would have seen the passengers in the windows; the ufo flew towards the direction of manhattan. when i notice the ufo fly over the car, i immediately got out to get a view of it but was no were to be seen. when i got back into my car i thought "well, you saw a 'triangle'".
trends: There have been no other sightings in Long Island City
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: Just happen to look up at the sky, which was overcasted, and witnessed a triangle shaped dark/black ufo overhead
